{"tid":1164147,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"9歲也被迫當性奴 上千北韓女性遭賣至支那","createTime":"2019-05-21T01:09:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T10:03:13.000Z","uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a6fde942f2a9722f2e69fd8d474a4db15ce2357f","tid":1164147,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpTR66og.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpTR66og.jpg&h=9c8bd081&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n關注北韓人權的組織「南韓未來倡議」（Korea Future<br />\nInitiative）今發表報告指出，有數以千計的北韓女人和女孩被賣到中國並且被迫從事性奴役。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpHaX6s7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpHaX6s7.jpg&h=ccf1d4c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「南韓未來倡議」發表報告指出，有數以千計的北韓女人和女孩被賣到中國並且被迫從事性奴役。（圖擷取自調查報告）<br />\n <br />\n根據《獨立報》（Independent）報導，「南韓未來倡議」今日發布的〈性奴隸：賣淫、網路賣淫和強迫結婚，在中國的北韓女人與女孩〉調查報告中顯示，這些來自北韓的女性從貧困、壓迫的北韓政權下逃出，經人口販子被賣去中國，在那裡她們被強迫從事性交易、性虐待、強迫結婚或網路賣淫，「直至她們耗盡自己的身體。」<br />\n <br />\n該研究指出，這個複雜的犯罪網絡組織，每年從販賣北韓女子的身體獲利1.05億美元（約新台幣33億元），而受害女性每次賣淫僅能拿到4美元（約新台幣145元），或是以146美元（約新台幣4700元）的代價被賣給他人當老婆。<br />\n <br />\n該報告的研究員指出，這些受害者年齡大多介於12至29歲之間，最小的只有9歲。許多人不止被賣掉一次，且離開北韓後的一年之中，至少遭受過一種性奴役。研究員表示，網絡賣淫的比重正不斷擴大。在作者發現的案例中就有1名年僅9歲的女孩，她遭性侵的畫面被網路直播。<br />\n <br />\n總部位於倫敦的「南韓未來倡議」是非盈利組織，該組織成立的目的在於幫助陷入危機的北韓人，並發布有關侵犯人權的報告。"},{"pid":"6b0aa30a04dc57ccce937b63989d591414008b9e","tid":1164147,"uid":35430,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:14:35.000Z","msg":"支那真係世界毒瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d604e5a0db6bc25230e67d19ea1d27e4894f95","tid":1164147,"uid":72009,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:15:15.000Z","msg":"唔敢comment<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b75b4e7e4b7ca5ff97d61a97f664b5d8e29cef","tid":1164147,"uid":64191,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:18:21.000Z","msg":"SJW: Sorry我地睇唔到，繼續狙擊恐同、父權、反素食、耶教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56327fbc97578198fb91ca38b30cf8248b4a62e5","tid":1164147,"uid":143499,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"f0b75b4e7e4b7ca5ff97d61a97f664b5d8e29cef","tid":1164147,"uid":64191,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:18:21.000Z","msg":"SJW: Sorry我地睇唔到，繼續狙擊恐同、父權、反素食、耶教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:24:15.000Z","msg":"聯合國繼續追擊毒撚對住漫畫蘿莉打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n北韓賣幾千個九歲小妹妹去中國做性奴?<br />\n<br />\nWFC<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2298a4bcdcf543299ec9aa8b673bdc3d66f62d5f","tid":1164147,"uid":196924,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:31:57.000Z","msg":"Korea Future Initiative is a London-based not-for-profit working to achieve accountability, dignity, and justice for exiled North Koreans.<br />\n<br />\n肯定係譯做「<span style=\"color: red;\">南韓</span>未來倡議」啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b673fe6ba78d2112725f9168265ce97cbd78c8b","tid":1164147,"uid":171866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T07:43:46.000Z","msg":"研究員表示，網絡賣淫的比重正不斷擴大。在作者發現的案例中就有1名年僅9歲的女孩，她遭性侵的畫面被網路直播。<br />\n<br />\nfbi呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"409518f9e85b0145203141a115c266336c1b1593","tid":1164147,"uid":13013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b673fe6ba78d2112725f9168265ce97cbd78c8b","tid":1164147,"uid":171866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T07:43:46.000Z","msg":"研究員表示，網絡